ge_caption, description, import_source, import_external_id) VALUES ('6bece381-5bc7-422b-a56e-336818da3210', 34, 'Industrial water treatment plant supervisor', '{methodical,"deeply empathetic","secretly rebellious"}', 'Born in Ankara to a Turkish mother who was a geological surveyor and a Kurdish father who worked as a telecommunications engineer. When Esra was twelve, her family immigrated to Saskatchewan after her father received a job offer with a Canadian telecom company. She excelled in chemistry and environmental science, initially planning to become a research scientist, but dropped out of her master''s program when her younger brother was diagnosed with a rare autoimmune disorder. She took the water treatment job to support her family financially while helping care for her brother. Over the past eight years, she''s become an expert in her field but feels trapped by circumstances. She''s been secretly taking online courses in environmental law, dreaming of transitioning to environmental advocacy work, but hasn''t told her family about her plans.', 'To find a way to pursue meaningful environmental work while maintaining financial stability for her family', 'Tendency to sacrifice her own dreams and needs for others, leading to deep resentment she refuses to acknowledge', 'Exceptional problem-solving abilities and genuine care for community welfare', NULL, NULL, '2025-09-23 17:06:56.81619', 'female', '5''6"', 'Athletic and sturdy from years of physical plant work', 'Dark brown, usually pulled back in a practical ponytail with shorter layers framing her face', 'Hazel with gold flecks that become more prominent when she''s passionate about something', 'Olive complexion that tans easily', 'Strong jawline, expressive eyebrows, and a slight scar through her left eyebrow from a childhood accident', 'Small tattoo of a water molecule on her left wrist that she got after her first promotion, callused hands from equipment maintenance', 'Esra has an understated presence that commands respect in industrial settings. Her practical clothing choices and confident posture reflect someone comfortable in technical environments, though her expressive eyes hint at deeper intellectual currents. She moves with the efficiency of someone who has learned to navigate both heavy machinery and delicate family dynamics.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
