ge_caption, description, import_source, import_external_id) VALUES ('fb2b8844-41ca-480d-b7c7-fe6fe32a766d', 34, 'Industrial hygienist specializing in pharmaceutical manufacturing safety', '{methodical,"quietly rebellious","emotionally guarded"}', 'Born to a Bolivian metallurgical engineer father and Bangladeshi textile factory manager mother who met during a UN industrial safety conference in Geneva. Raised primarily by her Bolivian paternal aunt in La Paz after her parents died in a factory explosion she witnessed at age 12. Immigrated to Canada at 17 on a scholarship, legally changed her hyphenated surname to honor both sides of her heritage. Has spent her career obsessively preventing industrial accidents, but struggles with survivor''s guilt and an inability to form lasting relationships due to her fear of sudden loss.', 'To prevent industrial disasters and protect workers, driven by the trauma of losing her parents in a preventable accident', 'Paralyzing perfectionism that sabotages relationships and causes her to micromanage others to an alienating degree', 'Unwavering moral compass and ability to see systemic problems others miss', NULL, NULL, '2025-09-23 17:18:06.515758', 'female', '5''4"', 'Compact and sturdy with calloused hands from early factory work', 'Black hair kept in a practical shoulder-length cut, often pulled back', 'Dark brown eyes that seem to constantly assess for potential hazards', 'Medium brown with golden undertones reflecting her mixed South Asian and Indigenous Bolivian heritage', 'Strong jawline inherited from her father, expressive eyebrows, small scar through her left eyebrow from debris during the factory accident', 'Chemical burn scar on her right forearm from her first job, small traditional Bangladeshi henna-style tattoo on her wrist her mother gave her', 'Zainab carries herself with quiet authority, her compact frame belying her inner strength. Her mixed heritage is evident in her features - the strong bone structure of her Quechua ancestry combined with South Asian coloring. She dresses practically in steel-toed boots and quality work clothes, her hands always clean but bearing the permanent stains and calluses of someone who works with chemicals and industrial equipment. Her watchful eyes seem to catalog every potential safety hazard in any room she enters.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '140 lbs', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Test Character Fixed Successfully', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
