s herself with quiet authority but flinches at unexpected loud sounds.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Human', 'mixed Welsh and Turkish heritage', 'she/her', 'travels between frontier towns', '', '{"deceased grandmother Cerys (Welsh hedge witch who taught her magic)","stepfather Mehmet Karaoglu (Turkish master blacksmith, still alive but estranged)","deceased birth parents (died in magical accident when she was young)"}', '', 'follows a syncretic blend of Celtic nature worship and Turkish folk beliefs about metalworking spirits', NULL, 'Tamsin', 'Karaoglu', NULL, NULL, 'Tam', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small village in the Welsh borderlands', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '189a6961-6711-4519-8e9b-103a6de3c84c', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Raised by her Welsh grandmother and Turkish stepfather after her birth parents died in a magical accident when she was three. Her stepfather, a master blacksmith, taught her the trade while her grandmother shared ancient Celtic magical traditions. At seventeen, she attempted to combine both arts to forge a weapon that could protect her small village from increasing monster attacks. The ritual went catastrophically wrong, killing her grandmother and leaving Tamsin with magical scars and a deep mistrust of her own abilities. She fled her village and now works as a traveling smith, using mundane metalworking to help others while suppressing her magical heritage.', NULL, NULL);
