[p][/p]
[p][/p]', NULL, '• 2000-2028: Born and raised in a small Nevada town, learned practical skills from his father who was a local sheriff''s deputy
• 2028-2031: Worked as a security guard at a mining facility when the Verdancy began spreading, met and married Corina.
• 2031-2036: Fled with other refugees to Espera with his family, established himself as settlement''s primary defender.
