• 2036: The defining tragedy • Corina murdered by Rootbound soldiers during what should have been a routine scavenging expedition
• 2036-Present: Devoted himself completely to security, became Security Keeper, raised Luca as single father while maintaining Espera''s defenses', '• Primary: Protect Espera and its people from all external threats, especially Rootbound
• Personal: Ensure his son Luca grows up safe and strong
• Professional: Maintain Espera''s defensive capabilities and strategic security
• Emotional: Seek justice/vengeance for Corina''s murder, though he channels this into protection rather than reckless pursuit', NULL, NULL, 'Fantasy', '33081217', '2025-10-07 16:58:56.429182', 'Man', '6''1"', 'Excellent fitness maintained through constant physical training and patrol work. Shows wear from years of hard living but remains in peak fighting condition for his age. Back pain is managed but persistent.', 'Dark brown, cropped short with grey streaks at temples', 'Steel-gray, sharp, scanning, deep-set under heavy brows', 'Weather-beaten olive skin, deeply tanned and scarred', '• Structure: Strong, angular jawline with high cheekbones
• Facial Hair: Well-maintained beard, trimmed close to his face
• Expression: Default stern expression that softens only around family
• Eyebrows: Thick and often furrowed in concentration
• Lips: Usually pressed in a firm line, rarely smiles', '• Major Scar: Left temple to jaw, from Rootbound combat
• Tattoo: Small saltfolk protection symbol on his right forearm
• Bearing: Military-straight posture despite never serving in formal military', 'Excellent fitness maintained through constant physical training and patrol work. Shows wear from years of hard living but remains in peak fighting condition for his age. Back pain is managed but persistent.', NULL, 'Values Old World standard gender identities.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '190 lbs', '', NULL, 'He/Him', NULL, NULL, NULL, '@[Espera](settlement:62fc36c4-cd05-48a8-a4b6-76c99a69d091)', 'Agnostic Pragmatist', NULL, 'Henrik', 'Rodenberg', '', '', '"The Wall"', 'Security Keeper/Defence Keeper', '', NULL, 'March 15th, 2000', 'Tonopah, Nevada', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Henrik is heterosexual, and is not strictly against other types of sexualities, but carries biases and stereotypes from the Old World that he grew up with as a child.', 'High school diploma, self-taught in tactics and weapons through necessity and voracious reading of salvaged military manuals. He has a penchant for learning about history, and carries a lot of knowledge about World War II because of his German-American heritage, and his grandfather having served in the war as a Nazi. He also has practical education in desert survival and settlement defence.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '• PTSD: From Corina''s murder and subsequent combat encounters
• Survivor''s Guilt: Believes he should have been with Corina on that fatal scavenging trip
• Hyper-vigilance: Constantly scanning for threats, difficulty relaxing
• Trust Issues: Betrayal by Martina''s family members created deep suspicion of others', '• Spatial Intelligence: Excellent at reading terrain, understanding defensive positions, and visualizing tactical scenarios
• Logical Reasoning: Strong analytical skills for threat assessment and strategic planning
• Pattern Recognition: Can identify behavioral patterns that indicate threats or deception
• Practical Intelligence: Highly skilled at problem-solving in real-world survival situations
• Limited Abstract Thinking: Struggles with theoretical concepts, prefers concrete, actionable information', '• Believes in harsh justice and decisive action
• Community survival justifies almost any action
• Good people deserve protection; those who threaten them deserve no mercy
• Strength and preparation prevent tragedy better than hope or mercy', NULL, '{"Fluent English, basic Spanish picked up from community members, tactical radio codes and hand signals, a few German words that were passed down through his family."}', NULL, '', 'Henrik''s skin is rough and weathered, with calluses built up from weapon handling and manual fortification work. Bears numerous small scars from desert survival and combat encounters.', NULL, '• Major Scar: Left temple to jaw, from Rootbound combat
• Tattoo: Small saltfolk protection symbol on his right forearm
• Bearing: Military-straight posture despite never serving in formal military', NULL, NULL, '• Enhanced Situational Awareness: Years of survival have given him almost supernatural ability to detect threats and changes in his environment
