• Competent: Skilled and thorough in all aspects of security and defense
• Reliable: Others can count on him completely
• Strategic: Thinks several steps ahead, excellent tactical mind', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '• Vengeful: Carries deep grudges, especially against Rootbound
• Suspicious: Struggles to trust new people or situations
