ge_caption, description, import_source, import_external_id) VALUES ('bb5cb308-435b-488f-bfe8-0ae658258b11', 34, 'saltstrider', '{methodical,cynical,protective,perfectionist,"secretly romantic"}', 'Born to a Lebanese-American petroleum engineer father and Salvadoran refugee mother who met at a university mathematics program in Houston. Raised by her paternal grandmother after her parents died in a car accident when she was twelve. Her grandmother, a former Beirut banking executive, taught her Arabic and instilled a deep appreciation for financial precision. Eliora excelled in mathematics but struggled with trust issues, leading her to a career where she hunts financial deceptions. She''s haunted by discovering her parents had hidden debts that nearly cost them their home, making her obsessively thorough in her work. Recently divorced after her ex-husband couldn''t handle her emotional unavailability, she now questions whether her protective walls have cost her genuine connection.', 'To expose financial predators and protect vulnerable people from the kind of hidden deceptions that devastated her childhood', 'Her compulsive need to uncover every secret and verify every detail makes her unable to trust or accept things at face value, sabotaging personal relationships', 'Unwavering determination to see justice done, combined with an intuitive ability to spot patterns others miss', NULL, NULL, '2025-09-24 10:28:58.591562', 'female', '5''4"', 'Compact and athletic from rock climbing, with strong hands from years of detailed work', 'Dark brown with premature silver streaks, usually pulled back in a precise bun', 'Amber with gold flecks, inherited from her father''s side', 'Warm olive complexion reflecting her mixed Middle Eastern and Central American heritage', 'Sharp cheekbones, expressive eyebrows, and a small scar through her left eyebrow from childhood', 'Small tattoo of Arabic numerals on her wrist representing her parents'' wedding date, and calluses on her fingertips from rock climbing', 'Eliora carries herself with quiet confidence, her amber eyes constantly analyzing her surroundings. Her mixed heritage shows in her warm olive skin and striking bone structure. She dresses professionally but practically, favoring tailored blazers and comfortable shoes. Her hands are always in motion when she thinks, and she has a habit of unconsciously touching the small Arabic numeral tattoo on her wrist when stressed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
