Modern Preservation Efforts: Aggressive data archiving, protection of research facilities, and recruitment of individuals with valuable knowledge or technical skills.', '{}', '• Standard Archive: A technical pidgin mixing English, scientific Latin, and military terminology.
• Clearance Codes: Numerical and alphabetic designation systems for security communication.
