[/ul]
[p][/p]
[p]Each of these members of the Council convene at @[The Keeper''s Den](Article:b2d3e4b5-2819-4a18-92b9-1a0c3938632b) to discuss trades, relationships, current events, political issues, resource management, policies, and more as they govern over @[Espera](Article:62fc36c4-cd05-48a8-a4b6-76c99a69d091) and its @[Saltfolk](Article:13c0c67e-37d3-41ed-94a8-2232e37843a0).[/p]
