INSERT INTO public.rituals (id, name, ritual_type, description, purpose, participants, requirements, steps, duration, location, timing, components, effects, risks, variations, genre, user_id, created_at, notebook_id) VALUES ('aab70f71-728d-4543-b32b-85dc1d8889e6', 'Oasis Harvest', 'other', '[p]The single most important event in @[Espera](Article:62fc36c4-cd05-48a8-a4b6-76c99a69d091)''s yearly calendar is the Oasis Harvest. The @[Saltfolk](Article:13c0c67e-37d3-41ed-94a8-2232e37843a0) make one large, organized excursion to the @[Furnace Creek](Article:8d87ea2b-f8b2-4a35-ab21-a87587525328) oasis as the only logical and efficient way to survive. This often happens in mid September, when the @[Date Palm](Article:3a012b82-20c3-4f20-9e24-73d46de6bd88) date palms are heavy with bunches of ripe, sugary dates and the @[Honey Mesquite Tree](Article:0c9eebe5-ddb0-441f-82d9-255760dceb16)''s pods are fully mature, dried, and ready to be collected from both the trees and the ground.[/p]
[p][/p]
[p]This is not a casual foraging trip; it is the settlement''s largest and most critical mobilization of the year. A large portion of the settlement temporarily moves from their main camp to the @[Furnace Creek](Article:8d87ea2b-f8b2-4a35-ab21-a87587525328) area to establish a secure, fortified processing camp surrounded by salt lines and using salted brine to clear a safe camping area.[/p]
[p][/p]
[p]The work is intense and non-stop. By combining the two harvests into a single, massive effort in one location, the @[Saltfolk](Article:13c0c67e-37d3-41ed-94a8-2232e37843a0) efficiently secure their primary sources of sugar (from dates) and carbohydrates/protein (from mesquite). This expedition is their annual insurance policy, the make-or-break event that determines if they have enough food to last through the winter and into the next year.[/p]
[p][/p]
[p]The Oasis Harvest is about maximizing efficiency, and since a large part of the settlement is already mobilized at the most resource-rich location in the valley, they use the opportunity to gather everything of value they possibly can. While the teams are harvesting the dates and mesquite, specialized groups are tasked with foraging and scavenging for crucial secondary resources.[/p]
[p][/p]
[p]The Oasis Harvest is a multi-faceted operation that secures the @[Saltfolk](Article:13c0c67e-37d3-41ed-94a8-2232e37843a0)''s two primary food staples while allowing them to procure the unique plant materials and invaluable processed goods of the Old World that are essential for tools, defence, and improving their quality of life.[/p]
[h2|5f1a972a-0e29-426c-b465-0288659d31df]Opportunistic Foods[/h2]
