arch at John Hopkins University, joined climate solution projects as young brilliant researcher\r\n• 2028-2031: Part of original Verdant compound development team, recruited by the IBCC as one of youngest senior researchers\r\n• 2032: At age 33, became Project Genesis leader and secretly volunteered as test subject, conceived Juniper\r\n• November 2032: Gave birth to Juniper, abandoned her at Espera''s salt line to hide from colleagues\r\n• 2032-2049: Continued Archive research while suppressing maternal instincts\r\n• 2049-2052: Quarantined and studied Juniper, attempting to harvest her immunity", "createdAt": "2025-10-07T16:58:55.023Z", "education": "Advanced degrees in genetics, bioengineering, and related fields. Likely PhD-level education from prestigious pre-Collapse institutions. Specialized training in Verdant biocode research.", "ethnicity": null, "etiquette": null, "farewells": null, "givenName": "Elan", "greetings": null, "hairColor": "blonde, grey streaks, pulled back into severe knot", "hairStyle": null, "interests": null, "languages": ["Fluent English, scientific Latin terminology, and multiple languages for international research collaboration."], "metaphors": null, "mutations": null, "strengths": "• Brilliant: Exceptional scientific mind capable of breakthrough insights\r\n• Dedicated: Unwavering commitment to her research goals\r\n• Disciplined: Maintains strict standards and methodologies\r\n• Resourceful: Finds ways to continue research despite obstacles\r\n• Strategic: Thinks long-term about species survival", "activities": null, "addictions": null, "conditions": null, "confidence": null, "familyName": "Thorne", "maidenName": "Porter", "mainSkills": "• Excellent At: Genetic research, biotech development, data analysis, maintaining emotional distance, strategic thinking, manipulating others for \"greater good\"\r\n• Poor At: Emotional connection, maternal instincts, understanding human psychology outside clinical framework, admitting mistakes, genuine remorse", "mannerisms": null, "middleName": "Judith", "motivation": "• Primary: Save humanity from extinction by the Verdancy at any cost\r\n• Scientific: Unlock the secrets of human-Verdant integration\r\n• Personal: Justify the sacrifice of her daughter through world-saving success\r\n• Professional: Maintain her position as leading Verdant researcher and prevent chaos", "notebookId": "0fe4e254-02d1-4a14-9046-6b3aefe17a89", "occupation": "[p][/p]\r\n[ul]\r\n- [b]Pre-Collapse[/b]: Senior researcher in biotech/genetic engineering\r\n- [b]IBCC Period[/b]: Lead researcher on Verdant compound development\r\n- [b]Current[/b]: Senior Archive scientist, Project Genesis director, Verdant research specialist\r\n[/ul]\r\n[p][/p]\r\n[p][/p]", "profession": null, "upbringing": null, "voicePitch": null, "accessories": null, "compliments": null, "dateOfBirth": "January 9th, 1999", "dateOfDeath": "", "description": "Dr. Elan Thorne carries the air of a woman who had long ago chosen precision over warmth. Her figure is spare, almost ascetic, her frame draped in a lab coat that looks less like clothing than an extension of her authority. The lines of her face are etched deep from years of squinting into harsh lighting and microscopes, the sharp planes of her cheekbones and jaw giving her a hawk-like severity. Her eyes, an unyielding gray, do not so much observe as dissect—every glance is a quiet incision, as though she is peeling back skin to reveal what lays beneath. She wears her blonde hair pulled back into a severe knot, not out of vanity but to remove all distraction, and the streaks of silver threading through it only accentuate the impression that time has been distilled into intellect rather than eroded into weakness. Her voice is deliberate, low, and steady, the kind that compels silence in a room without needing to rise above it, each word carrying the weight of record and decree. Around her, the scent of antiseptic seems to linger, as though she herself was an extension of the Archive’s sterile halls—unmoved, untouchable, and utterly unyielding.", "hairTexture": null, "investments": null, "personality": null, "toneOfVoice": null, "wealthClass": null, "workHistory": null, "catchphrases": null, "dependencies": null, "extroversion": null, "familialTies": null, "famousQuotes": "• \"You''re not a person anymore • you''re a vector.\"\r\n• \"This isn''t personal • it''s about species survival.\"\r\n• \"I wasn''t supposed to be your mother. I was supposed to be your creator.\"\r\n• \"Clean. Clinical. Scientific.\"", "heightDetail": null, "hygieneValue": null, "imageCaption": "ChatGPT Image Aug 29, 2025, 12_13_57 PM.png", "importSource": null, "keyEquipment": null, "mentalHealth": "• Undiagnosed Narcissistic Personality Disorder and Autism\r\n• Professional Guilt: Responsibility for creating the disaster that destroyed civilization\r\n• Maternal Suppression: Psychological damage from abandoning her daughter\r\n• Obsessive Compulsion: Unable to stop researching despite repeated failures\r\n• Isolation: Emotional detachment from human connections", "placeOfBirth": "Baltimore, Maryland", "placeOfDeath": "", "rememberedBy": null, "behavingStyle": null, "commonPhrases": null, "facialDetails": null, "lackingSkills": null, "proficiencies": null, "secretBeliefs": null, "speakingStyle": null, "typicalAttire": "• Style: Clinical and authoritative • pristine lab coat over dark clothing\r\n• Equipment: Always carries data tablets, research instruments\r\n• Condition: Immaculate appearance maintained as psychological armour", "articleContent": null, "characterFlaws": "• Emotionally Detached: Treats people as specimens rather than individuals\r\n• Morally Compromised: Willing to sacrifice individuals for perceived greater good\r\n• Obsessive: Cannot let go of failed experiments or relationships\r\n• Manipulative: Uses others'' emotions and loyalties to achieve her goals\r\n• Self-Justifying: Rationalizes cruel actions as necessary sacrifices", "faci