wenties, he’s lean and rangy from days spent tracking game across the salt flats, his movements carrying the quiet grace of a predator. His skin, olive like his father’s, is bronzed deeper by long hunts under the relentless desert sun. His dark hair, shaggier than Henrik would approve of, often falls into his eyes—eyes that are mahogany than hazel, alive with a daring edge and the untamed hunger of someone still testing the boundaries of his world.\n\n\n\n\n\nWhere Henrik radiates control, Luca carries a raw, restless energy. He wears practical scavenged leathers reinforced with bits of scrap metal and hide, tailored not for intimidation but mobility. Strapped across his back is his hand-crafted bow, worn smooth from constant use, the fletching on his arrows feathered with scavenged bird plumage—small marks of pride in his craftsmanship. At his belt, tied with a rough leather cord, hangs a bighorn sheep horn charm, a token from his first great hunt, polished by years of his hand brushing against it like a grounding talisman.\n\n\n\n\n\nHis face holds the tension of dual inheritance: Henrik’s carved jaw and serious brow, softened by a warmth that flickers more easily than his father allows himself to show. When he smiles—rare but striking—it carries the reckless joy of someone who has not yet been broken by loss, though the weight of survival presses close. He is the embodiment of a new generation: trained by tragedy, armed with pragmatism, but still carrying within him the possibility of something freer, less hardened than what came before.", "hairTexture": null, "investments": null, "personality": null, "toneOfVoice": null, "wealthClass": null, "workHistory": null, "catchphrases": null, "dependencies": null, "extroversion": null, "familialTies": null, "famousQuotes": "", "heightDetail": null, "hygieneValue": null, "imageCaption": "ChatGPT Image Aug 30, 2025, 04_19_39 PM.png", "importSource": null, "keyEquipment": null, "mentalHealth": "", "placeOfBirth": "", "place